Package: contisweep
Title: Continuous Sweep Prevalence Estimation
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Kevin",
           family = "Kloos",
           email = "kevinkloos@hotmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6980-4259"))
Description: Implements the Continuous Sweep quantifier for prevalence estimation with uncertainty quantification. Provides functions for:
    - Optimal hyperparameter selection (pdelta) using grid search.
    - Variance estimation via basic and advanced variance equations.
    - Confidence interval calculation.
